      input#free-email-1(type='email' name='free-email' placeholder='Enter your email...')
      #signup-email-error-1.error-message Please input a valid email
    #signup-button-1.btn.btn-primary Try it free
  .go-demo
    | Or you can
    a
      span Get a demo
